\pard\plain \fi720\sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What do you think you\u8217\'92re doin\u8217\'92!?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This shout came from right behind Mandri\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s ear, and it startled him near to death. He turned and gave the angry Hrk who\u8217\'92d uttered it a sheepish shrug, but the Hrk was already set on the talon raking the stone.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s true!\u8221\'94 the man shouted, and at once, Mandri was surrounded by a crowd of excited faces haloed by torchlight. Each Hrkan eye was as wide as his own. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Out of the way!\u8221\'94 Pyetle shouted as he elbowed his way through the crowd. Once at the wall, he marveled at the sight of Solraheen\u8217\'92s defacement.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He held his hand up against it.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He splayed his fingers so that they settled in the monstrous scrape.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He briefly searched the rest of the wall for a sign of any further indignity, but it was clean. This put another notch into Pyetle\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s already furrowed brow. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93A single scrape,\u8221\'94 he muttered.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Slate, standing at the edge of the crowed, said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93A single scrape,}{\f1\fs24\b0\i1\cf1  precisely placed.}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 was intentional. That great scouring claw did not sign rage, it signed intelligence. It was a mark of meaning. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Can this demon think?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If it can think, it can scheme!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 What to do.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Sudden flash of concern.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Scour the crowd.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Where is the giant!?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Silence.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri searched for Ayram\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s towering frame, a black mast in that clutch of white robes, but none was there.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Who was on him!?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 A Vessel in the first square wavered for a moment, then stepped forward. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It was Fally,\u8221\'94 he said, anxiety rippling his words. \u8220\'93He was watching the giant.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Where is he!?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I think they\u8230\'85Sir, I suggest they\u8217\'92ve gone ahead.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Gone }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1\cf1 ahead}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 ?\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 Pyetle countered. Most ridiculous attempt to divert his fury into some sort of poorly action.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Rage upon his people.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 No one answered. Quiet.  Ayram\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s inexplicable absence was somehow more disquieting than if he were here and . }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Pyetle cornered Elrahet. He towered over her as as the darkness towered over him.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Where is he?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Elrahet grunted.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You will tell me where he has gone.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I suppose that he has fled,\u8221\'94 she said simply. \u8220\'93As so should you.\u8221\'94}
\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\pard\plain \fi720\sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What do we do? Should we go back?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 To hear the words suggesting retreat, a flash of certainty hardened Pyetle\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s face. He broke back through the crowd to confront Elrahet\u8217\'92s wizened glare. \u8220\'93Which way is the beast?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Down.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1}